  Welcome to your persistent development environment!

  📦  Tools Available:
      • kubectl, helm, k9s, kustomize - Kubernetes tooling
      • docker - Container management
      • git, gh - Version control
      • terraform, aws - Infrastructure as Code
      • go, node, python - Development runtimes
      • tmux, screen, zsh - Terminal multiplexers
      • vim, nano - Text editors
      • claude - AI-powered development assistant

